    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once very hot, add the <strong>coated cauliflower</strong> to the pan[s] and cook for 10-12 min or until golden and crispy on the outside and tender on the inside – this is your <strong>crispy cauliflower</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>crispy cauliflower</strong> to a plate, set aside and reserve the pan for later</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1618242100252-x200.jpg",
